{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"c2d9f0c855","title":"致卫立煌电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"2df7cc9186","index":0,"year":1949,"month":10,"day":15,"articleId":"c2d9f0c855"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji27","name":"毛泽东全集第27卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/27-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji27":{"comments":[{"id":"444d303730","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"c2d9f0c855","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"张枫，即饶彰风，当时任中共中央华南分局港澳工作委员会委员。"},{"id":"771c215592","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"c2d9f0c855","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指卫立煌1949年10月3日给毛泽东的电报。电报全文是：“先生英明领导，人民革命华获辉煌胜利；从此全中华人民得到伟大领袖，新中国富强有望，举世欢腾鼓舞，竭诚拥护。煌向往夷心尤为雀跃方丈。敬电驰贺。朱副主席、周总理请代申贺忧。"}],"contents":[{"id":"8f2fbcae18","type":"title","text":"致卫立煌电","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"c2d9f0c855"},{"id":"444d303730","type":"paragraph","text":"张极转卫立煌将军：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"c2d9f0c855"},{"id":"771c215592","type":"paragraph","text":"西江电诵悉，极为感谢。谨此奉复。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"c2d9f0c855"},{"id":"31ce759a2f","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"c2d9f0c855"},{"id":"ee948de1ab","type":"paragraph","text":"西册","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"c2d9f0c855"},{"id":"ed95bd4a69","type":"paragraph","text":"[I]卫立煌，1948年任国民党政府军东北“剩汇”总司令部总司令。沈阳解放前夕回到南京，被蒋介石软禁。1949年初出走香港。他给毛泽东的电报是从香港发出的。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"c2d9f0c855"}],"page":{"id":"fbfe6db6c1","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"c2d9f0c855","start":424,"end":424}}}},"__N_SSG":true}